@jbowman1107 It requires a PR to the `django_filters` repo. I did a hack look like this earlier and it works (though for sure it isn't elegant).   

```python
from enumfields.fields import EnumFieldMixin
from django_filters.filters import ChoiceFilter
from django_filters.filterset import BaseFilterSet


def patch_filterset(klass):
    old_filter_for_lookup = klass.filter_for_lookup

    def new_filter_for_lookup(cls, field, lookup_type):
        if isinstance(field, EnumFieldMixin):
            choices = tuple((e.value, label) for e, label in field.choices)
            return ChoiceFilter, {'choices': choices}
        return old_filter_for_lookup(field, lookup_type)

    klass.filter_for_lookup = classmethod(new_filter_for_lookup)

patch_filterset(BaseFilterSet)
```

